    "created_at": "2015-03-02T19:43:02Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-03-02T19:43:11Z",
    "body": "This worked perfectly fine two weeks ago. Raw pointers were not Send but you could opt into Send when you knew that it's safe. There seems to be no reason to remove that feature.\n",
