    "created_at": "2015-03-03T16:55:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-03-03T16:55:40Z",
    "body": "The RFCs you linked seem to be completely unrelated to Send and the PR that implemented this restriction only referred to the OIBIT RFC. In the OIBIT RFC it says:\n\n```\n1. move Send and Share out of the language entirely and into the standard library\n```\n\nHow would a pure library trait in any way affect a language item such as the Drop trait?\n",
